  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5965042/" class="title-link">姓氏是中国历史的密码</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5965042"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2536300/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2536300-26.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2536300/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">司马白羽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-05-17"
      class="main-meta">2013-05-17 20:16:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5965042_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         	姓氏在全世界都存在，但中国的姓氏文化最为系统，最有脉络可寻，甚至可以说是一部历史的密码。《钱文忠讲解百家姓》是一部通俗而易懂的书，虽然并不够深入，但却开启了人们重新认识自己姓氏的大门。 	 	中国的姓氏起源非常早，可以追溯到母系社会，上古八姓：姚、妫、...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
